\id 2PE - Ndwewe Bible Version
\h 2 Petili
\toc1 Lihamba lya ubhili lya kuhuma kwa Petili
\toc2 2 Petili
\toc3 2 Pet
\mt2 Lihamba lya ubhili kuhuma kwa
\mt1 Petili
\imt1 Ulongolelo
\ip Lihamba lya ubhili kuhuma kwa Petili lingulubhulilwa kukita likityekwa na Nndumila Petili, peni asomi atangalo bha manjubha agha bhanguhyubhalila ng'obhe kukita ayo ndo hoto. Yinguhyubhalika kukita mundu yungi kakityeka lihamba ali mbole ya Petili. Ywakatyekite kangulongela kukita mwene kakibhegha nnyimiho kwa maho ghake ya kya ulami ghwa Yesu na kyanalumu pala pakaghalambukite kibhungi, Nlyango ghwa 1:17-18. Handa Petili kakityeka lihamba ali, yingubhoneha kukita kakityeka pakabheghite ku Loma mu uhiko ghwa ngungwa ya mbinda mabhoko sita mbole ya kubhelekwa kwa Kilisito pakali na kuhwegha Petili. Kangi Petili kangulikema lihamba ali ndo lya ubhili. Nlyango ghwa 3:1, Petili bhubho kangulikema lihamba ali ndo lihamba lyake lya ubhili lyeni lyakatyekite mbole ya lihamba lyake lya ulongohi. Kakiatyekela bhandu bhoha bhaanhyubhalila Kilisito.
\ip Petili kakityeka lihamba ali ngati kabhayonjokehe mwoyo bhaanhyubhalila Kilisito bhatame ubhumi ghwa maha na kuakinya kukita bhakotoke kubhatughila mahundo gha ahunda bha uhwangi, Nlyango ghwa 2. Kangubhayonjokeha mwoyo pakilongela kukita bhabhayuyuhe bhandu bhaalongela kukita Yesu kakabhaalila kubhuya. Mbole yake kangubhinilila kukita Chapanga kangukabhalila ng'obhe ngati kangupala bhandu bhoha bhalopoleghwe, Nlyango ghwa 3:8-9. Aki ndo kihokonyo kya kutama ubhumi ghwa maha, Nlyango ghwa 3:14.
\iot Ghaabheghite
\io1 Petili kangulimanyia na kangubhamanyiha bhala bhakabhatyekela lihamba, Nlyango ghwa 1:1-2.
\io1 Mbole kanguaghombela bhatame ubhumi ghwa maha kiyaha Chapanga kanguatangatila kulama abho Nlyango ghwa 1:3-21.
\io1 Mbole kanguakinya ya kya ahunda bha uhwangi na kulongela kukita kila kyabhapala kubhatula kuuhiko bhaabwituka ahunda bha uhwangi, Nlyango ghwa 2:1-22.
\io1 Mbole kanguyomolela kwa kuayonjokeha mwoyo ahyubhalila kutama ubhumi ghwa maha na kulibhika kala kwa kubhuya kwa Yesu, Nlyango ghwa 3:1-17.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Lihamba ali linguhuma kwa nenga Simoni Petili, nndumitumi na nndumila ghwa Yesu Kilisito.
\p Nungubhatyekela mwenga bhene kwa umaha ghwa Chapanga na nlopohi ghwetu Yesu Kilisito, mmemwa uhyubhalilo ghulaghula ghwa utopelo handa ghutunemelitwe twenga.
\v 2 Nungubhapalila umaha na uhihimilo ngenju mu kummanya Chapanga na Yesu Bambo ghwetu.
\s1 Nkemwa na kulingwa na Chapanga
\p 
\v 3 Kwa makakala ghake gha uchapanga, Chapanga katupegha milando yoha yituyipalite ngati tutame ubhumi ghwa kuntundamila Chapanga kwa kummanya ywombe ywakatukemite tulilunge muukulu na umaha ghwake.
\v 4 Kwa njila ayi, katupegha ninganilo ngulu na hya utopelo hyene hyakatulaghiliti. Kya habhu hingututangatila kuhileka uhanjabhano hiibheghite munnima na kubhegha papamu na uchapanga.
\v 5 Kya habhu, nkakalike kwa nnyonjokeha uhyubhalilo ghwenu nnyonjokehe na umaha na umaha ghwenu nnyonjokehe na umanyi,
\v 6 na umanyi ghwenu nnyonjokehe na uyukuto, na uyukoto ghwenu nnyonjokehe na ulimbililo, na ulimbililo ghwenu nnyonjokehe kuntundamila Chapanga,
\v 7 na uhokamo ghwenu kwa Chapanga nnyonjokehe na upalo ghwa kiulongo na upalo ghwa kiulongo nnyonjokehe na upalo,
\v 8 handa pammegha na numbo ahi hyoha, maabhegha atotoho ng'obhe hangi maalepelwa ng'obhe kutenda gha maha mu kummanya Bambo ghwetu Yesu Kilisito,
\v 9 peni mundu ywa nga numbo ahyo ndo ywangalola, kaahotola ng'obhe kubhona kutali naywo kalibhalila kukita kutandila makachu kakiyohwa kala ulemwa ghwake.
\v 10 Kya habhu, makaalongo bhangu, mukatende ubhinililo kyanalumu ngati kulutenda alwo lukemo na kuhaghulighwa na Chapanga lubheghe nnando ghwa ngungulima muubhumi ghwenu. Pantenda habhu maahobha ng'obhe,
\v 11 kwa njila ayi maanemelelwa utekulo nkulu pakuyingila kuubhutwa ghwa Bambo na nnopohi ghwetu Yesu Kilisito.
\p 
\v 12 Na kya habhu, ndaghendelela kubhakulungilwa maghenda maghenda milando ayi, hata payibhele manya kala na ntengeleka mu hoto ghumughukingamite.
\v 13 Nenga nungubhona nnando ghwa shaliya kwa nenga, manjubha ghoha pandama apa pannima, kubhayonjokeha makala na kubhakulungilwa kwa kya milando ayi,
\v 14 kiyaha nungumanya kukita mmili ghwangu aghu hamba ndaghuleka, handa Bambo ghwetu Yesu Kilisito pakanng'ombelite pekupeku.
\v 15 Hino, ndaabhinilila kwa likaho mbole ya kuhwegha nenga nhotole kughakulungwa agha maghenda maghenda.
\s1 Mayimiho bha Ukulu ghwa Kilisito
\p 
\v 16 Manjubha patubhahundite kwa kya kuhika kwa Ukulu ghwa Bambo ghwetu Yesu Kilisito, tukilidumbila ghweka nga mihumu ya uchenjelo chenjelo, ngati tukiubhona Ukulu ghwa kuhika kwa Bambo ghwetu Yesu Kilissito kwa meho ghetu twabhene.
\v 17 Kiyaha kakikingama uhokamo na ukulu kuhuma kwa Tate Chapanga, pala lilobhe palinhikilite kuhuma kwa ywombe ywakabheghite Ukulu Nkulu, paliyuhwanika, “Ayu ndo Mwana ghwangu mpalo yunuuyelelitwe naywo.”
\v 18 Kangi twenga twabhene tukiliyihwa lilobhe alyo kuhuma kunane manjubha patubheghite papamu naywo kunane kwa kila kukitumbi kya Chapanga.
\p 
\v 19 Kangi, twenga tubhegha na lilaghilo lya kulyaghila muno lya umbuye ghwa Chapanga, na mwenga mungutendite maha handa munng'ungilite, kiyaha ndo handa lung'ali palilangalika palubhindo mbaka kucheghe ndondwa ya ngeha paying'anyima mu myoyo yenu.
\v 20 Kuchweha kwa agho, peni nkulungwe kukita kahone mundu ywakapala kufwambula mwene ulondohi ghuubheghite mu umbuye ghwa Chapanga,
\v 21 kiyaha kahone lilagho lya ulondohi ghwa Chapanga liibhukana na mapalo gha anamundu, ngati bhandu bhakikambuka ulondohi pabhalongohitwe na Nhuki ghwa Chapanga.
\c 2
\s1 Ahunda bha Uhwangi
\p 
\v 1 Bhakibwituka mambuye bha uhwangi nkati ya bhandu, na ubhwabhu abhu ahunda bha uhwangi bhaabwituka nkati yenu. Bhandu abho bhaayingiha mahundo mahakataho na kunkiluka Bambo ywakabhakombolite, na kwa njila ayi bhaayambukiha makanjaghano gha kanongola.
\v 2 Kangi bhandu atangalo bhayitughila milando yabhe ayi mihakataho, na kubhukana na bhombe atangalo bhayiligha njila ya hoto.
\v 3 Kwa tama yabhe hakataho bhaalimokolela motelo kuhuma kwa mwenga kwa kubhaghombela mihumu ya uhwangi. Peni toso yabhe yikilandamihwa kutandila makachu na kukanjaghanwa kwa bhombe kungubhalindila.
\p 
\v 4 Kiyaha andumitumi bha kunane kwa Chapanga pabhatendite na ulemwa, Chapanga kakiabhonela luhungu kata, ngati kakibhataghila ku mwoto ghwangahimika kwene bhabhopwa na bhangulindila linjubha lya toso.
\v 5 Ubhwabhu abhu handa Chapanga kakilubhonela kata luhungu nnima ghwa makachu, ngati kakiyegha ngumbwa ngulu ya machi unani mwa nnima ghwa bhandu bhala bhanga kuntundamila ywombe, peni Chapanga kakinlopoha Nuhu ywakannandamihite maha papamu na bhandu bhangi saba.
\v 6 Hila hila Chapanga kakiyikeha milima ya bhandu bha ku Sodoma na ku Gomola, kakiyikanjaghana kwa mwoto, kakiyitenda yibhe mihwano ya ghala ghene ghaabhahikila bhandu bhala bhanga kuntundamila Chapanga.
\v 7 Kakinnopoha Lutu, mundu ywa maha, ywene ywakahyononohitwe munu na ng'endelo hakataho ya bhandu abho akiluka.
\v 8 Kiyaha Lutu kakitama munkati ya bhandu abho, kwa manjubha matangalo, Lutu kakihyononeka mu mwoyo ghwake ntwihiliko pakayihwite mandendelo ghabhe mahakataho.
\v 9 Kya habhu, Ywombe kangumanya kya bhula pakapala kualopoha bhandu bhaantundamila na bhula pakubhabhika ahokelo ngati kabhahyatule linjubha lya toso,
\v 10 kyanalumu bhala bhanu bhaatughila tama hakataho ya mmili na kuupughana utabhala ghwa Chapanga.
\p Bhandu abho ndo akiluka na bhanakulidumba, bhanguhiligha na kuihokamila ng'obhe hibhumbe hiibheghite na ukulu bhaabheghite kunani,
\v 11 peni hata andumitumi bha kunane kwa Chapanga bhaabheghite na makakala na utabhala kupitingana kwa ahunda bha ahwangi, kubhaligha ng'obhe paabhakokela paulongolo ghwa Bambo.
\v 12 Bhandu abho bhangukiligha kyohele kyanga kukimanya. Ndo handa anyama bhanga mahala, Bandu abho bhangunmanya ng'obhe yula ywaanliga, bhene bhangubhelekwa na kuuhiko bhangukamulwa na kuhinjwa. Nabho handa anyama bhaakanjaghanwa bhubho.
\v 13 Kangi bhaakamuhwa himbamanda kwa kya himbamanda hyaabhaiyeghelite bhangi. Bhanguyelelwa kutenda tama hyabhe ya uhakata pamuhi pa pee, habhu bhombe ndohanda mamelena atebhaho bhanguyegha honi mu chekwa yenu, paanlyegha papamu nabho kunu bhangughendelela kuyelelwa na njila yabhe ya uhwangi.
\v 14 Meho ghabhe ghalembukila ungongola, na tama yabhe ya kutenda ulemwa. Bhangubhalongoha bhandu ayoyobhalo mu myoyo mbaka kuntambo. Myoyo yabhe yihyobhelela kulyegha ukwapukwapu, na bhakotoleghwa na Chapanga.
\v 15 Bhayileka njila yiighololekite, bhapotoka na bhayitughila njila yakayitughilite Balaamu mwana ghwa Beoli ywene kakinoghelwa kumokola ngalabha kwa ndendelo ya kuatendela bhandu uhakata,
\v 16 peni kakilakalilwa kubhukana na ulemwa ghwake, kaputa ywangalongela, kakilongela kwa lilobhea lya mundu na kuukanikiha ubhugha bhugha ghwa mbuye aywo.
\p 
\v 17 Bhandu abha ndo handa kinyopa kiyumite, handa mahundi ghanakuyangaluhwa na likusi, matamo ghabhe ghabhikwa mu ukunguungweta.
\v 18 Kwa tama yabhe hakataho bhangubhanyegheleha bhala manjubhaagha bhabhuka mu bhala bhaatenda mahakataho.
\v 19 Bhangubhalagha bhandu bhangi kukita bhaabhegha ng'obhe abhandwa peni bhombe ndo abhandwa bha ulemwa, kiyaha mundu ndo nbhandwa kwa kilibhi kyoheli kila kiintabhala.
\v 20 Bhandu bhapuluchukite kuhuma mu ulemwa ghwa nnima, kwa njila ya kummanya Bambo na Nnopohi ghwetu Yesu Kilisito, peni handa pabhaghubhuyila ulemwa ghwabhe, utamo ghwabhe ghwaabhegha nhakata kupitingana kandahi.
\v 21 Yingabheghite mbaha kwa bhene kuyimanya ng'obhe njila ya maha, kihyengo kya kuyimanya njila ayi ya maha na mbole kughaleka ngwiliho yiibhaghulitwe kwa kya Chapanga yaakamuhitwe.
\v 22 Yilandana telatela kwa bhombe na nongelo ayi ya hoto yiilongela, “Galu kaghakapula malokoko ghake mwene” na nongelo yingi yingulongela habhu, “Lighulubhe ywakaghululitwe kangughalabhuka mumandika!”
\c 3
\s1 Naghilo ya kuhika kwa Bambo
\p 
\v 1 Maaghanja bhangu, ali ndo lihamba lyangu lya ubhili linubhatyekela. Mumahamba agha mabhili nungutenda kuyigha kughahwimula mahwacho ghenu gha maha ghaannogheha Chapanga.
\v 2 Nungupala nkulungwe malagho ghaalongelitwe na ambuye bha Chapanga bha makachu na yila ngwilikiho ya Bambo na nnopohi yimuyikingamite kukindila kwa andumila bhenu.
\v 3 Kukali kwa ghoha, mmanye kukita manjubha gha kuuhiko bhaahika bhandu bhanakuyuyuha na bhaatama kwa kutughila tama yabhe bhene,
\v 4 pabhalongela, “Kilisito kakilagha kukita kaabhuya! Bhuli, lelo kabhegha kwoki? Kutandila pabhahweghite akaatate bhetu Mihalo yaabhegha bhulabhula, kila kilibhi kyaghendelela bhula bhula handa payibhele kalongohi pa ubhumbo.”
\v 5 Bhandu abho kya likaho lyabhe bhakilibhala kukita pamakachu Chapanga kakilkambuka lilagho ghweka na nnima na kunani kukibhumbwa. Kakibhumba nnima kuhuma mu machi na kwa njila ya machi,
\v 6 na kangi kukindila kwa machi agho, nnima ghwa makachu ghala ghukikanjaghanwa kwa ngubwa ngulu ya machi.
\v 7 Kangi kwa lilagho alyo Chapanga kakibhika kunani na nnima ghwa hinu kwa kya kuyochwa mwoto. Kubhikwa kwa kya linjubha lya toso na kukanjaghanwa kwa bhandu bhanga kuntundamila Chapanga.
\p 
\v 8 Peni maalongo bhangu, nkotoke kulibhala lilagho ali, kukita kwa Bambo linjubha limu ndo handa ngungwa elufu na ngungwa elufu ndo handa linjubha limu.
\v 9 Bambo kangukabhalila ng'obhe kuyitwihilika nagho yakayilaghite handa bhandu bhangi pabhahwachila kukabhalila. Mwene kabhegha na ulimbililo ghwa kya mwenga, kiyaha kalema mundu ywoheli kakanjaghanwe peni kangupala kila yumu kalipetule.
\p 
\v 10 Peni linjubha lya Bambo lyahika handa mundu mwihi. Linjubha alyo kunane kwayangaluka kwa lulundumo lukulu na hibhumbe hiibheghite amwo hyayochwa mwoto, nnima na hilibhi hyoha hya munnima hyakanjaghanwa.
\v 11 Kiyaha kila kilibhi kyakanjaghanwa habhuhabhu, bhuli mwenga mungunoghwa mmeghe bhandu bhakya bhuli? Mungunoghwa ntame ubhumi ghuubhaghulitwe kwa kya Chapanga,
\v 12 pannindila na kulipala lihike kanongola lila linjubha lya Chapanga. Linjubha alyo kunane kwa Chapanga kwayochwa mwoto na kukanjaghanwa, na hibhumbe hyake hyayangaluka kwa lupyupo.
\v 13 Peni handa pakalaghite twenga tungulindila Kunani kwa hyono na nnima ghwa hyono mweni bhandu bhangutenda ghweka ghala ghaannogheha Chapanga.
\p 
\v 14 Na kya habhu makaaghanja bhangu, kiyaha muyililindila milando ayi, nkakalike mmeghe bha maha kyanga limele ebu libhaya na mmeghe na uhihimilo muulongolo ghwake.
\v 15 Mungunoghwa kubhegha na ulimbililo ghwa Bambo kukita ghuna ulopohi handa bhula nnongo ghwenu mpalo Paulo pakabhatyekelite kwa mahala makulu ghakakingamite kwa Chapanga,
\v 16 handa pakalongelite mu mahamba ghake ghoha. Milando yngi mu mahamba agha ndo manonopo kughamanya. Milando ayi abhughabhugha na bhanauyumbilo mu kunhyubhalila Kilisito bhangughahobheha handa pabhaghahobheha matyeko ghangi gha Chapanga. Na kya habhu bhalipalila kukanjaghanwa kwa bhene.
\p 
\v 17 Peni maaghanja bhangu mmanya kala nhalo aghu. Mulikingikihe nkotoke kuhobhehwa na mahokelo gha bhandu abha bhanga kutughila malaghilo, maaponeka kuhuma ku umaha ghwenu na kulepelwa kukamulila hoto.
\v 18 Peni nng'endelele kukula mu umaha na kummanya Bambo na Nnopohi ghwetu Yesu Kilisito. Ukulu ghubhegha kwa ywombe, hino na hata kwa manjubha ghoha! Ayi mwika.
